00:55:19.930 --> 00:55:21.230
And it scans the barcode.

00:55:21.310 --> 00:55:23.000
It goes out on the internet,
downloads a ton of

00:55:23.000 --> 00:55:25.960
information about that item,
and puts it into this catalog

00:55:26.420 --> 00:55:27.300
where you can browse through it.

00:55:27.300 --> 00:55:28.440
You can search.

00:55:28.460 --> 00:55:30.900
You can check stuff out to
