00:55:30.900 --> 00:55:32.640
and keep track of all your stuff.

00:55:32.680 --> 00:55:36.080
So it's really nice.

00:55:36.370 --> 00:55:38.940
It's a really simple interface
and this is really important.

00:55:38.940 --> 00:55:42.110
We wanted to make a program
that anyone could use.

00:55:42.240 --> 00:55:47.740
Not something that hardcore
collectors would only like or

00:55:47.870 --> 00:55:49.540
