New toolbar.

01:08:02.220 --> 01:08:03.040
Boom.

01:08:03.390 --> 01:08:04.590
New sidebar.

01:08:04.590 --> 01:08:06.580
Let's look at that sidebar for a second.

01:08:06.580 --> 01:08:08.430
Notice how there's the Your Computer tab.

01:08:08.430 --> 01:08:09.220
There's one tab.

01:08:09.230 --> 01:08:10.130
Don't have one tab.

01:08:10.130 --> 01:08:11.860
Tabs are supposed to have, you know.

