01:15:46.900 --> 01:15:48.100
My .Mac account?

01:15:48.360 --> 01:15:51.600
You know, get rid of the close buttons,
folks.

01:15:51.630 --> 01:15:54.600
They don't mean what
users think they-- I mean,

01:15:54.600 --> 01:15:56.540
users are getting used to
it because they're adapting,

01:15:56.540 --> 01:16:02.220
but quite honestly,
it doesn't make any sense in

01:16:02.220 --> 01:16:02.220
